Ver 0.0.1

Test version to get an idea on gameplay mainly in the early (or late game). This alters a few levelled lists and items so will have conflicts with other things that do the same.

Quick list of features in this version:

 - BAL: Rebalanced all weapons (armour soon)
 - BAL: Rebalanced all arrows (NOT FINAL)
 - BAL: Tweaked potion values to have lower magnitude over a longer duration - encourages smarter potion usage
 - BAL: Increased enemy health values across the board by about 1.75x
 - BAL: Added new bleed perk to all 'Rune' type weapons
 - BAL: Food values tweaked
 - BAL: Integrates Valravn as a baseline for Combat Balancing
 - BAL: Default race values tweaked
 - BAL: Standardises all difficulty values (Will add easier and harder later)

 - CNT: Implements Shadow Steel Reimagined
 - CNT: New foods and harvestables with crafting recipes

 - QOL: Adds prefixes to all foods by type
 - QOL: Adds prefixes to all Potions by type
 - QOL: Renames all potions to be much clearer by type and changes all Tiers to be a numbered system for more transparency and readability

Requires only SPID 
Sould load very late in LO
